  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You point at one creature you can see within range, and the single chime of a dolorous bell is audible within 10 feet of the target. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or take [[/damage 1d8 necrotic]] damage. If the target is missing any of its Hit Points, it instead takes [[/damage 1d12 necrotic]] damage.</p><p><strong>Cantrip Upgrade.</strong> The damage increases by one die when you reach levels 5 ([[/damage 2d8 necrotic]] or [[/damage 2d12 necrotic]]), 11 ([[/damage 3d8  necrotic]] or [[/damage 3d12 necrotic]]), and 17 ([[/damage 4d8 necrotic]] or [[/damage 4d12 necrotic]]).</p>",
